      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "41.72.71.21.22.31.32 "
                                          to   w-prs-tfu-psr-wst      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo a rielaborazione stringa            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     prs-tfu-psr-100.
       prs-tfu-psr-999.
