           move      w-rig-snx-3qt (1)    to   rf-osr-snx-3qt         .
           move      w-rig-dec-3qt (1)    to   rf-osr-dec-3qt         .
           move      w-rig-qta-a03 (1)    to   rf-osr-qta-a03         .
           move      w-rig-dec-prz (1)    to   rf-osr-dec-prz         .
           move      w-rig-sgl-vps (1)    to   rf-osr-sgl-vps         .
           move      w-rig-dec-vps (1)    to   rf-osr-dec-vps         .
